name: Stay Out Of My Personal Space
name_original: Stay Out Of My Personal Space
description:
Made for one hour game jam 278 with the theme "space".

WASD to move, when someone is in your personal space you take damage.

Try to survive for as long as possible.   

Made by myself and https://onehourgamejam.com/?page=author&author=corrie

Check out corrie's itch for his other submissions to one hour game jam.
